WEBVTT

01:42.950 --> 01:45.990
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.060 --> 01:48.990
[Episode 31]

01:49.090 --> 01:51.130
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

01:51.910 --> 01:52.470
I don't care about the price.

01:52.490 --> 01:53.500
You negotiate it.

01:53.630 --> 01:54.310
But it has to be paid in full,

01:54.350 --> 01:55.170
and it's paid today.

01:55.190 --> 01:56.190
I gotta go.

01:56.190 --> 01:57.610
I'm accompanying Tang Jie for her prenatal check-up.

02:02.660 --> 02:04.740
No way, this is so amazing.

02:04.810 --> 02:05.500
Yes.

02:06.480 --> 02:07.200
Zhong?

02:08.039 --> 02:09.050
Zhong?

02:10.759 --> 02:11.510
Honey,

02:11.910 --> 02:13.030
you called me. What's wrong?

02:13.630 --> 02:14.350
Pay the fee.

02:20.210 --> 02:21.750
Pay the fee, Zhong.

02:23.070 --> 02:24.390
Pay the fee. I'll go pay it.

02:28.750 --> 02:29.510
What's wrong?

02:31.750 --> 02:32.590
I just think Zhong

02:32.590 --> 02:33.910
has been acting weird lately.

02:35.340 --> 02:36.500
How?

02:38.200 --> 02:39.820
He's been going out to meet people every day

02:39.840 --> 02:41.329
and coming home very late.

02:41.360 --> 02:42.910
When he comes home, he just sits on the sofa,

02:42.930 --> 02:43.560
without saying a word,

02:43.590 --> 02:44.390
completely still.

02:45.540 --> 02:47.790
Is he under a lot of stress at work?

02:47.810 --> 02:49.740
I thought so before.

02:49.950 --> 02:50.980
But you know what?

02:51.020 --> 02:52.710
He calls people every day behind my back

02:52.740 --> 02:54.390
and even brings his phone into the shower.

02:55.070 --> 02:55.860
You...

02:56.350 --> 02:57.500
checked his phone?

02:58.740 --> 03:00.580
Of course.

03:00.750 --> 03:02.210
But I found nothing.

03:02.390 --> 03:03.310
He deleted everything.

03:04.510 --> 03:05.400
Well, did he actually delete everything,

03:05.430 --> 03:06.550
or was there nothing there to begin with?

03:07.870 --> 03:09.590
Stop guessing.

03:09.700 --> 03:10.310
Really?

03:11.210 --> 03:12.080
He is not cheating on me?

03:13.570 --> 03:15.210
Zhong is so nice to you.

03:15.240 --> 03:16.950
How could he possibly cheat on you?

03:17.350 --> 03:19.360
It's all because you're pregnant now,

03:19.670 --> 03:21.820
and your hormones are all over the place, you know?

03:21.910 --> 03:23.570
You're paranoid.

03:23.780 --> 03:24.940
Stay happy.

03:26.030 --> 03:28.070
Just talk things through with him together.

03:28.790 --> 03:29.710
I know. I know.

03:29.790 --> 03:30.520
Stop talking about me.

03:30.590 --> 03:31.329
Go back to work.

03:32.390 --> 03:33.530
Communicate, okay?

03:33.750 --> 03:34.430
Stay happy.

03:34.470 --> 03:35.910
Okay, okay.

03:35.970 --> 03:41.040
[Every Step of Pregnancy Counts]

03:36.310 --> 03:37.280
So cheesy.

03:41.220 --> 03:42.110
What did you say?

03:43.190 --> 03:44.520
1.6 million yuan?

03:44.910 --> 03:46.310
I bought that apartment so my parents

03:46.350 --> 03:48.050
could come help take care of the baby, you know?

03:48.430 --> 03:49.240
How could they suddenly cut the price

03:49.240 --> 03:50.030
by 400,000 yuan?

03:53.670 --> 03:54.390
Fine, fine.

03:54.590 --> 03:55.890
1.6 million yuan it is.

03:56.230 --> 03:57.570
Can they transfer the money today?

03:59.390 --> 04:00.360
Next week won't work!

04:00.390 --> 04:01.150
I'm waiting for money

04:01.180 --> 04:02.570
to pay my employees!

04:04.490 --> 04:05.420
1.6 million yuan.

04:05.590 --> 04:06.970
1.6 million yuan, deal.

04:07.070 --> 04:08.070
Transfer the money today,

04:08.150 --> 04:09.070
or forget it.

04:10.480 --> 04:11.080
Alright, alright.

04:11.230 --> 04:11.920
Wait, wait,

04:11.950 --> 04:12.430
Dalu?

04:13.340 --> 04:14.960
Delete our chat history.

04:15.160 --> 04:16.470
Don't let Tang Jie find out.

04:16.880 --> 04:17.640
Okay.

04:18.190 --> 04:18.829
That's it.

04:28.190 --> 04:28.910
Honey.

04:34.640 --> 04:36.290
There was nothing at the funeral home either.

04:36.770 --> 04:37.290
Yes.

04:37.540 --> 04:38.760
We went to the funeral home,

04:38.909 --> 04:39.990
and we found a staff member

04:40.030 --> 04:40.970
who seemed quite suspicious.

04:41.000 --> 04:42.820
We plan to start with him.

04:43.550 --> 04:45.260
Over the past few times, I've noticed

04:45.470 --> 04:47.110
that Li Ruonan is very sensitive

04:47.190 --> 04:48.390
about her mother's information.

04:49.380 --> 04:50.520
Every time I bring it up,

04:50.909 --> 04:51.990
she gets really worked up,

04:52.870 --> 04:53.870
but she just won't say anything.

04:56.550 --> 04:57.460
Don't worry.

04:57.630 --> 04:59.070
As long as we can find Yan Mei,

04:59.090 --> 05:00.610
she will definitely tell us.

05:01.510 --> 05:02.870
Okay, let's do it step by step.

05:03.680 --> 05:04.470
By the way...

05:07.740 --> 05:09.380
Yu Bofeng is also in Chengzhou.

05:09.870 --> 05:10.870
We found

05:10.890 --> 05:11.990
that he has been following us

05:11.990 --> 05:12.750
since yesterday.

05:13.030 --> 05:14.220
What does he want?

05:14.790 --> 05:16.230
Should we contact the local police

05:16.250 --> 05:17.060
and have him controlled?

05:17.490 --> 05:18.760
There's no need for that.

05:20.330 --> 05:21.580
I think

05:21.870 --> 05:23.230
if he's really passing messages

05:23.270 --> 05:24.670
to Wen Peng,

05:25.150 --> 05:26.160
once he realizes

05:26.190 --> 05:26.830
we've found

05:26.830 --> 05:27.960
some key clues,

05:28.000 --> 05:29.470
they'll definitely take action.

05:30.150 --> 05:31.030
At that point,

05:31.050 --> 05:31.990
we can act.

05:32.030 --> 05:32.659
Okay.

05:33.320 --> 05:34.450
Be careful.

05:34.830 --> 05:36.140
If anything happens, let me know at any time.

05:36.350 --> 05:37.470
Okay, don't worry.

05:37.590 --> 05:38.310
We'll keep in touch.

05:46.100 --> 05:46.780
Well...

05:47.390 --> 05:47.900
Honey,

05:49.070 --> 05:50.990
this is roughly how things are.

05:59.190 --> 06:00.670
Are you really going to disband the company?

06:02.900 --> 06:04.430
Don't worry about it.

06:04.450 --> 06:05.880
You're pregnant now.

06:06.820 --> 06:07.680
Well...

06:08.550 --> 06:09.720
just disband it.

06:10.340 --> 06:12.050
Didn't you always say I was keeping

06:12.430 --> 06:14.080
a bunch of idle people?

06:14.470 --> 06:15.750
Might as well take this chance

06:16.330 --> 06:17.470
and disband it.

06:19.510 --> 06:21.430
Their monthly salaries add up to hundreds of thousands.

06:22.490 --> 06:24.190
Things are different now.

06:24.830 --> 06:26.070
We're having a baby.

06:26.590 --> 06:27.870
We need to be more careful with money.

06:31.180 --> 06:31.980
It's okay.

06:54.440 --> 06:55.990
I still have some money on this card.

06:56.550 --> 06:58.060
It's enough to support your company for a while.

06:58.630 --> 06:59.270
No, honey,

06:59.310 --> 07:00.150
what are you doing?

07:00.180 --> 07:01.550
This is the money that Mom gave you as your personal savings.

07:01.590 --> 07:03.030
I-I-I can't take this money.

07:03.680 --> 07:05.120
No, take it back.

07:05.140 --> 07:07.220
We're married. What's mine is yours.

07:09.790 --> 07:10.390
Zhong.

07:10.930 --> 07:12.280
Those long-serving employees

07:12.310 --> 07:13.690
have been with you for so many years.

07:14.750 --> 07:16.180
They all have families to support.

07:16.870 --> 07:18.070
If you lay them off,

07:18.110 --> 07:19.190
how will they survive?

07:20.560 --> 07:21.280
Besides,

07:21.310 --> 07:22.940
even if you want to dissolve the company,

07:23.110 --> 07:24.510
you still have to compensate them according to their length of employment,

07:25.070 --> 07:25.630
right?

07:27.310 --> 07:27.910
Take it.

07:31.070 --> 07:32.010
Take it.

07:38.930 --> 07:40.110
Do you remember

07:40.900 --> 07:41.820
how you established

07:41.909 --> 07:42.590
the company back in the day?

07:46.159 --> 07:46.880
Back then,

07:46.909 --> 07:48.070
you had no background.

07:49.340 --> 07:51.090
Your family didn't give you any money,

07:51.350 --> 07:52.270
and no one helped you.

07:53.550 --> 07:54.830
It was all you,

07:55.560 --> 07:56.870
working with all your men,

07:57.310 --> 07:58.480
slowly turning a small

07:58.510 --> 07:59.590
post-production company

08:00.190 --> 08:01.540
into what it is today.

08:04.320 --> 08:06.170
You've made it through all the hardships before,

08:06.950 --> 08:07.830
so why are you afraid now

08:07.870 --> 08:08.630
of only this small matter?

08:11.350 --> 08:12.260
Yes, I shouldn't be afraid.

08:12.290 --> 08:13.620
Why should I be afraid?

08:14.510 --> 08:16.530
I have the best wife in the world,

08:17.430 --> 08:18.150
my baby,

08:19.340 --> 08:20.780
and a group of

08:21.070 --> 08:22.110
loyal men who've been with me

08:22.130 --> 08:23.100
throughout this journey.

08:25.350 --> 08:26.710
It's okay. I can handle it.

08:30.060 --> 08:30.880
Zhong.

08:36.659 --> 08:37.600
If it comes to it, we can always

08:37.630 --> 08:38.470
start over.

08:40.750 --> 08:41.640
I'll be there for you.

08:42.760 --> 08:43.929
Thank you, honey.

08:44.790 --> 08:46.360
I'll go out to get some business tomorrow.

08:48.850 --> 08:50.090
Everything will be fine.

08:58.000 --> 08:58.940
Of course,

08:59.350 --> 09:01.030
this is an investment on my part.

09:02.030 --> 09:02.970
In the future,

09:03.040 --> 09:04.490
pay me back with interest.

09:07.510 --> 09:08.270
No, honey,

09:08.290 --> 09:09.740
didn't you say, "What's mine is yours"?

09:17.300 --> 09:20.410
[China Construction Bank]

09:20.480 --> 09:25.370
[Yileaiju Agency]

09:20.550 --> 09:21.520
Look at this apartment.

09:21.550 --> 09:22.980
It has three bedrooms, one living room, and two bathrooms.

09:23.150 --> 09:23.750
It's 90 square meters in size

09:23.750 --> 09:24.720
and costs only 1.57 million yuan.

09:24.750 --> 09:25.800
It's a really good deal.

09:26.000 --> 09:27.090
Take a look.

09:27.490 --> 09:28.110
Or, I have

09:28.110 --> 09:29.130
many other apartments.

09:28.750 --> 09:32.680
[Yileaiju Agency]

09:29.270 --> 09:30.280
Would you like to buy an apartment?

09:30.310 --> 09:31.580
I'll introduce it to you if you'd like.

09:31.610 --> 09:33.140
I'll think about it.

09:34.070 --> 09:34.590
Okay.

09:36.650 --> 09:38.890
[Yileaiju Agency]

09:37.530 --> 09:39.630
Ma'am, are you buying a house or looking for a house?

09:44.110 --> 09:45.330
I'll go in and take a look.

09:45.630 --> 09:46.070
Sure.

09:46.100 --> 09:46.600
Thank you.

09:46.630 --> 09:47.300
Let me show you.

09:47.880 --> 09:49.030
How much have you lost?

09:51.160 --> 09:52.460
That much?

09:52.700 --> 09:54.620
Zhong's company has been dragged down.

09:58.470 --> 09:59.670
It's all my and Jiang Chengyi's fault.

09:59.710 --> 10:01.480
Well, we've dragged you into this...

10:02.010 --> 10:03.310
Don't think like that.

10:03.530 --> 10:04.820
How is it your fault?

10:05.070 --> 10:06.180
It's all that Wen Peng's fault.

10:06.230 --> 10:07.330
He's shameless and despicable.

10:07.360 --> 10:08.470
I just don't understand

10:08.510 --> 10:09.830
how he can be so bad.

10:09.850 --> 10:10.750
He even tried to harm you

10:10.790 --> 10:11.350
in the hospital the other day.

10:11.390 --> 10:12.630
Is he a psychopath or what?

10:12.690 --> 10:13.770
Alright, alright.

10:13.920 --> 10:14.950
Don't you know

10:14.950 --> 10:15.870
you're pregnant?

10:15.890 --> 10:17.010
Calm down.

10:19.270 --> 10:20.320
What are you going to do

10:20.350 --> 10:21.270
next?

10:22.430 --> 10:23.870
What else can we do?

10:24.190 --> 10:25.760
I've shown the contract to the lawyer.

10:25.910 --> 10:27.150
The odds of winning aren't big.

10:28.470 --> 10:29.230
Even if we go to court,

10:29.270 --> 10:30.430
it'll take years.

10:30.760 --> 10:32.110
The company can't afford that either.

10:33.670 --> 10:35.550
I'm thinking of selling the house

10:35.590 --> 10:36.960
to help the company get out of financial difficulties.

10:37.110 --> 10:37.670
Then we can

10:37.670 --> 10:38.890
start over.

10:39.270 --> 10:40.350
Where will you live

10:40.390 --> 10:41.670
if you sell the house?

10:42.030 --> 10:43.470
My mom's place.

10:43.790 --> 10:44.630
You have no idea.

10:44.710 --> 10:45.470
Ever since I got pregnant,

10:45.550 --> 10:46.270
my mom has been insisting

10:46.310 --> 10:47.070
that I go stay with her.

10:47.110 --> 10:48.030
I'll take this opportunity

10:48.050 --> 10:48.840
to accompany her.

10:54.830 --> 10:56.110
I have 100,000 yuan here.

10:56.130 --> 10:57.170
I'll transfer it to you.

10:57.350 --> 10:58.400
No need, no need.

10:58.430 --> 11:00.150
Why do I need your money?

11:01.070 --> 11:02.370
I don't have more than that either.

11:02.470 --> 11:03.280
That's all I have.

11:03.390 --> 11:04.150
I have some extra

11:04.200 --> 11:05.080
to live well.

11:05.310 --> 11:06.770
You can take this for now to tide you over.

11:15.380 --> 11:15.990
Okay.

11:16.550 --> 11:19.280
When I have more money,

11:19.320 --> 11:20.670
I'll pay you back with interest.

11:20.700 --> 11:22.350
Then pay me a little extra.

11:22.520 --> 11:23.040
Okay.

11:23.390 --> 11:24.400
Let me toast to you with tea.

11:24.470 --> 11:26.210
Hope you can rise again.

11:28.100 --> 11:29.690
Take care of yourself.

11:30.070 --> 11:31.390
Stay in a good mood.

11:31.470 --> 11:33.940
Don't be dragged down by these things.

11:34.400 --> 11:35.050
Don't worry.

11:46.340 --> 11:47.250
I'm sorry

11:47.360 --> 11:48.360
for letting you come all the way here for nothing.

11:48.510 --> 11:50.210
Not at all, thank you for your help this time.

11:50.350 --> 11:51.060
No, no, no.

11:51.510 --> 11:53.020
We've just found the body.

11:53.110 --> 11:54.440
The gender and age match,

11:54.510 --> 11:55.150
but unfortunately, it's not the person

11:55.190 --> 11:55.990
you are looking for.

11:58.010 --> 11:58.550
How about this?

11:59.110 --> 12:00.720
I know some people at the funeral home.

12:00.740 --> 12:01.530
Later, I'll ask around for you.

12:03.590 --> 12:05.070
There's a staff there

12:05.110 --> 12:06.900
named Wang Yifan.

12:07.110 --> 12:08.090
Do you have any impressions of him?

12:08.310 --> 12:09.150
Wang Yifan...

12:09.190 --> 12:09.870
Are you talking about

12:09.870 --> 12:11.110
that temporary worker, Wang Yifan?

12:11.440 --> 12:11.870
Yes.

12:11.950 --> 12:12.790
-Yeah, yeah.
-That man.

12:12.810 --> 12:13.410
He...

12:13.960 --> 12:15.110
honestly, is not that good.

12:15.120 --> 12:15.830
Back in school,

12:15.220 --> 12:22.100
[Police]

12:15.910 --> 12:16.780
he was always getting into fights

12:16.870 --> 12:17.870
and even ended up in jail several times.

12:18.510 --> 12:19.470
He didn't work after graduation.

12:19.630 --> 12:20.680
He used to hang around

12:20.710 --> 12:21.340
with gangs in the back alleys of Chengzhou

12:21.430 --> 12:22.190
and idle around.

12:22.600 --> 12:23.630
His father

12:23.630 --> 12:24.630
works at the funeral home.

12:24.980 --> 12:25.730
So his father has no choice

12:25.870 --> 12:26.630
but to let him

12:26.630 --> 12:27.710
work as a temporary worker there.

12:29.790 --> 12:30.480
That's it.

12:30.750 --> 12:31.910
Thanks for coming all the way here.

12:31.940 --> 12:33.410
Call me if you need anything.

12:33.590 --> 12:34.390
Okay, thank you.

12:35.830 --> 12:36.390
Thank you.

12:42.590 --> 12:43.030
Let's go.

12:43.310 --> 12:45.950
[Public Security]

12:43.320 --> 12:43.850
Okay.

12:49.150 --> 12:49.720
Yan,

12:49.900 --> 12:51.220
there's been a surge of patients in the ER.

12:51.240 --> 12:52.500
We're swamped.

12:52.520 --> 12:53.630
I'll get changed now. You go ahead.

12:53.670 --> 12:54.590
Okay, I'll head over first.

12:57.920 --> 12:59.000
Yan.

12:59.470 --> 13:00.030
Auntie,

13:00.070 --> 13:01.190
what are you doing here?

13:02.080 --> 13:03.640
I came to you for something.

13:04.120 --> 13:05.780
Next time, just give me a call.

13:05.810 --> 13:07.580
I was supposed to rest today.

13:07.750 --> 13:09.190
Otherwise, you would have come here for nothing.

13:09.280 --> 13:10.240
Okay, okay.

13:10.480 --> 13:11.910
I'm here on a whim.

13:16.100 --> 13:17.430
I went to see Peng.

13:19.950 --> 13:21.880
I waited outside his building for a long time,

13:22.620 --> 13:23.860
but he still didn't want to see me.

13:26.660 --> 13:27.800
So...

13:31.310 --> 13:32.430
I want to...

13:33.270 --> 13:33.910
trouble you

13:33.930 --> 13:35.410
to give this to Peng for me, okay?

13:36.100 --> 13:37.020
Auntie,

13:37.300 --> 13:38.390
last time...

13:38.670 --> 13:39.830
I know.

13:39.990 --> 13:40.830
Last time,

13:41.820 --> 13:44.140
asking you to arrange a meeting between me and Peng

13:45.030 --> 13:46.430
must have put you in a difficult position.

13:47.590 --> 13:49.650
I was too impatient.

13:51.590 --> 13:53.020
These things can't be rushed.

13:54.270 --> 13:55.550
We need to take it step by step.

13:56.230 --> 13:57.820
Peng has a problem with me...

13:59.040 --> 14:00.660
and he's hostile to Chengyi too.

14:01.430 --> 14:04.070
So after thinking it over...

14:05.290 --> 14:07.390
You are one of his friends, after all.

14:07.790 --> 14:08.920
So, I can only

14:08.940 --> 14:10.560
count on you for this.

14:11.070 --> 14:12.310
I-It's nothing.

14:12.350 --> 14:12.950
It's...

14:14.050 --> 14:15.200
I've written down some things

14:15.200 --> 14:16.190
I want to say to Peng

14:17.190 --> 14:18.390
in this letter.

14:19.410 --> 14:20.490
Auntie.

14:21.230 --> 14:22.540
Even if I give it to him, he...

14:24.240 --> 14:25.550
he may not accept it.

14:27.500 --> 14:28.740
I-I know.

14:29.550 --> 14:30.150
Just...

14:30.210 --> 14:31.800
Just try it for me, please.

14:32.350 --> 14:34.960
If it doesn't work, I'll think of another way.

14:36.230 --> 14:37.970
I'll leave the letter here.

14:38.150 --> 14:38.750
Well,

14:38.770 --> 14:40.180
aren't you busy?

14:40.220 --> 14:41.480
I won't keep you any longer.

14:41.590 --> 14:43.820
If you're free, come home with Chengyi.

14:44.590 --> 14:45.160
Let me know what you want to eat,

14:45.190 --> 14:46.630
and I'll cook for you, okay?

14:47.670 --> 14:48.950
Auntie, take care of yourself.

14:51.840 --> 14:53.240
I'm off then.

15:04.820 --> 15:07.260
[To Peng]

15:12.420 --> 15:16.840
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

15:14.340 --> 15:15.680
My mom went to see you again?

15:15.990 --> 15:18.840
Yes, she asked me to send a letter.

15:19.510 --> 15:21.090
I don't even know what to do.

15:21.310 --> 15:22.180
It's okay.

15:22.100 --> 15:24.850
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

15:22.370 --> 15:23.480
Don't worry.

15:23.810 --> 15:24.660
I'll send it for you.

15:25.230 --> 15:25.930
You...

15:26.240 --> 15:26.750
You...

15:26.780 --> 15:27.990
You send it... well...

15:28.070 --> 15:29.230
Leave it to me.

15:29.750 --> 15:30.700
Give me the letter,

15:30.910 --> 15:31.790
and I'll send it tomorrow.

15:33.020 --> 15:34.640
Don't get into any conflict with him.

15:34.920 --> 15:35.790
Don't worry.

15:36.110 --> 15:37.000
I can do it.

15:38.350 --> 15:41.070
Are you working overtime tomorrow night?

15:41.470 --> 15:42.150
What's wrong?

15:43.350 --> 15:44.220
Nothing.

15:44.390 --> 15:45.510
If you don't work overtime,

15:45.540 --> 15:46.840
come pick me up, will you?

15:46.950 --> 15:47.550
Sure.

15:49.830 --> 15:50.710
That's all.

15:52.150 --> 15:52.670
Bye.

15:53.380 --> 15:57.100
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

16:00.380 --> 16:01.800
What's with all this?

16:08.470 --> 16:09.220
Bofeng,

16:09.600 --> 16:10.310
where are you?

16:12.510 --> 16:13.240
Say something.

16:13.270 --> 16:14.270
You're driving me crazy.

16:15.540 --> 16:16.930
I came to Chengzhou.

16:18.510 --> 16:19.670
Why did you go to Chengzhou?

16:19.990 --> 16:20.590
Because I heard

16:20.630 --> 16:21.790
that Yu Zheng and others came to Chengzhou.

16:22.380 --> 16:23.630
So I followed them here.

16:24.230 --> 16:25.390
How many times have I told you

16:25.390 --> 16:27.080
to stay calm?

16:27.140 --> 16:28.240
I'll arrange everything.

16:28.270 --> 16:28.990
Why do you have to

16:29.030 --> 16:30.020
come to Chengzhou for them?

16:30.120 --> 16:30.550
Peng,

16:30.570 --> 16:31.270
this matter

16:31.310 --> 16:32.590
has already implicated you.

16:32.610 --> 16:33.630
You've already done

16:33.630 --> 16:34.670
so much for me.

16:35.700 --> 16:36.950
Let me handle the rest,

16:36.990 --> 16:37.390
okay?

16:40.930 --> 16:42.320
You don't need to do anything now.

16:42.400 --> 16:44.320
Listen to me and come back.

16:44.350 --> 16:45.040
Peng,

16:45.710 --> 16:47.030
I didn't come here in vain these days.

16:48.020 --> 16:48.950
I found that they

16:48.950 --> 16:49.670
went to the funeral home  yesterday

16:49.670 --> 16:51.000
and then to the police station.

16:51.240 --> 16:52.630
They seem to be investigating something.

16:52.670 --> 16:53.270
There are too many of them.

16:53.310 --> 16:54.750
I didn't have a chance.

16:55.230 --> 16:56.200
Give me two more days.

16:56.430 --> 16:57.110
Two days.

16:58.020 --> 16:58.950
I'll come back to you

16:58.990 --> 17:00.110
right after I've handled things here.

17:00.850 --> 17:01.600
I'm hanging up, Peng.

17:03.790 --> 17:04.390
Hello?

17:13.190 --> 17:13.930
Mr. Wen,

17:14.290 --> 17:15.270
Jiang Chengyi is here.

17:33.890 --> 17:35.250
Your mother wrote this to you.

17:40.470 --> 17:41.160
[To Peng]

18:02.110 --> 18:03.060
Whatever.

18:04.150 --> 18:05.330
I've delivered it anyway.

18:11.230 --> 18:12.070
Zhong is in a terrible situation

18:12.110 --> 18:12.950
because of you.

18:14.590 --> 18:15.750
Let him go.

18:16.460 --> 18:17.970
What do you mean, Captain Jiang?

18:19.820 --> 18:21.670
My cooperation with Zhong

18:21.710 --> 18:23.580
was clearly laid out in black and white.

18:23.670 --> 18:24.950
If he ends up losing everything,

18:24.950 --> 18:26.110
what does that have to do with me?

18:29.590 --> 18:31.270
Don't get others involved...

18:33.310 --> 18:34.720
in our grievances.

18:36.030 --> 18:36.950
That's just how it is.

18:41.700 --> 18:43.140
Captain Jiang, have you ever thought

18:43.620 --> 18:45.650
that you might be the source of all this misfortune?

18:47.050 --> 18:48.040
As long as

18:48.070 --> 18:49.030
you're with Lu Yan,

18:49.510 --> 18:51.630
more people are likely to

18:51.670 --> 18:52.540
encounter misfortune.

18:55.030 --> 18:56.030
Are you...

18:57.470 --> 18:58.510
threatening me?

18:59.090 --> 19:00.310
I'm just guessing.

19:01.630 --> 19:04.040
And under certain circumstances,

19:04.180 --> 19:04.950
we are

19:04.990 --> 19:05.950
still somewhat brothers.

19:06.560 --> 19:07.830
We're just having a chat.

19:11.180 --> 19:11.870
You'll have a chance

19:11.870 --> 19:13.030
to have a proper chat with me.

19:29.750 --> 19:31.640
[Hello, Peng. When you open this letter, I believe you miss me too.]

19:31.720 --> 19:36.080
[The ways I've failed you as a mother—even a lifetime
wouldn't be enough to make up for them.]

19:31.720 --> 19:36.080
[All these years, I've never given up looking for you.]

19:42.350 --> 19:47.290
[Being happy and healthy is what matters most. Take a break whenever you're tired.
I'll always love and support you.]

19:42.350 --> 19:47.290
[When you read this letter, you may still hate me, but that's okay.
Mom just wants you to live well—that's all that matters.]

19:47.290 --> 19:50.750
[Love you, Mom]

20:18.250 --> 20:21.930
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

20:22.110 --> 20:22.870
Yan.

20:23.170 --> 20:25.200
I'll be boarding soon.

20:25.620 --> 20:27.000
You don't have to come pick me up.

20:27.030 --> 20:28.400
I can just grab a taxi home.

20:28.430 --> 20:29.070
It's okay.

20:29.110 --> 20:30.230
I'll get off work on time today.

20:30.270 --> 20:31.180
Wait for me.

20:31.350 --> 20:31.950
Have a safe flight.

20:36.080 --> 20:37.030
You're having surgery

20:37.070 --> 20:38.550
in a couple of days.

20:38.970 --> 20:40.400
You need to be careful with your diet.

20:40.590 --> 20:41.390
Think about

20:41.390 --> 20:42.030
what you want to eat now.

20:42.110 --> 20:42.750
Once you're restricted,

20:42.750 --> 20:43.920
you won't be able to eat it.

20:44.670 --> 20:46.280
I don't have much of an appetite.

20:46.350 --> 20:47.730
I'm feeling airsick from the flight

20:47.790 --> 20:49.450
and still not feeling well.

20:50.320 --> 20:51.640
Come on.

20:51.830 --> 20:52.670
I'll only have

20:52.710 --> 20:54.360
a small surgery, half an hour at most.

20:54.390 --> 20:55.870
Why make me come all the way here?

20:56.070 --> 20:56.870
Is it really necessary?

20:57.070 --> 20:58.030
Of course, it's necessary.

20:58.100 --> 20:58.660
Let's go.

20:59.050 --> 21:04.630
[Times Square Station]

21:05.210 --> 21:07.570
Though it's a small surgery, it still needs general anesthesia.

21:08.970 --> 21:10.550
Why should I be afraid?

21:10.590 --> 21:11.230
I have my daughter

21:11.230 --> 21:13.090
to watch over me.

21:13.870 --> 21:15.350
I don't have that kind of mental strength.

21:15.370 --> 21:16.520
I won't be the one operating.

21:17.050 --> 21:17.990
What do you mean?

21:18.330 --> 21:19.500
Are you stupid?

21:19.520 --> 21:20.230
Isn't this

21:20.270 --> 21:22.120
a perfect opportunity for you to toughen up?

21:22.220 --> 21:22.720
Come on.

21:22.830 --> 21:24.060
Do it to your mother.

21:24.100 --> 21:25.770
How can you make such a joke?

21:27.840 --> 21:28.580
Fine.

21:28.610 --> 21:29.800
No more jokes.

21:30.600 --> 21:32.030
Let me tell you something serious.

21:32.950 --> 21:34.890
Since I'm here,

21:35.260 --> 21:36.690
there's something I want to take care of

21:36.790 --> 21:37.840
while I'm here.

21:38.240 --> 21:39.300
What is it?

21:40.420 --> 21:41.340
I

21:41.950 --> 21:44.090
want to meet Jiang's parents.

21:45.480 --> 21:47.200
It's too sudden.

21:47.270 --> 21:48.690
Sudden?

21:49.390 --> 21:51.470
Including your time apart,

21:51.500 --> 21:52.240
you've been together on and off

21:52.270 --> 21:54.180
for over ten years, right?

21:54.870 --> 21:56.580
Shouldn't you be hurrying things up by now?

21:56.870 --> 21:57.550
Seriously.

21:57.560 --> 21:58.190
Besides,

21:58.390 --> 21:59.380
even after getting married,

21:59.400 --> 22:00.320
you can still date,

22:00.350 --> 22:00.870
right?

22:00.910 --> 22:01.430
I...

22:01.510 --> 22:03.110
I'm not urging you to have kids.

22:03.130 --> 22:03.750
Mom.

22:03.790 --> 22:04.640
You really

22:05.310 --> 22:06.920
always act on every whim that comes to mind.

22:06.990 --> 22:08.820
You were so hard on him last time,

22:08.870 --> 22:10.730
and now you're here trying to speed things up.

22:10.750 --> 22:12.460
How can this be the same as last time?

22:12.480 --> 22:13.810
That was the first time I met him;

22:13.830 --> 22:15.110
should I have to

22:15.140 --> 22:16.520
test him out?

22:18.300 --> 22:19.470
You're not in a hurry,

22:19.550 --> 22:20.990
but I have to.

22:22.930 --> 22:24.130
How about this?

22:24.270 --> 22:24.910
You

22:24.930 --> 22:26.280
help me set up a meeting

22:26.310 --> 22:26.990
with Jiang's mom.

22:27.300 --> 22:29.270
The two of us can have a good chat.

22:29.350 --> 22:30.000
It's best

22:30.030 --> 22:31.230
we can set the wedding date

22:31.270 --> 22:32.210
for you two.

22:32.390 --> 22:33.110
That way,

22:33.190 --> 22:34.110
I can

22:34.110 --> 22:35.070
check this off my list of worries.

22:35.110 --> 22:35.810
Mom,

22:35.990 --> 22:37.920
something's going on with his family right now.

22:38.070 --> 22:39.030
It's not a good time

22:39.050 --> 22:39.870
to bring it up.

22:40.620 --> 22:41.620
What happened?

22:43.110 --> 22:43.770
Well.

22:43.880 --> 22:45.170
I can talk to her, taking this chance.

22:45.230 --> 22:45.750
Maybe I can

22:45.830 --> 22:46.960
offer her some advice.

22:48.350 --> 22:49.550
My dear mother,

22:49.580 --> 22:50.750
please stay out of this.

22:51.110 --> 22:51.740
Fine,

22:51.870 --> 22:52.800
I will!

22:53.710 --> 22:54.390
But you have to

22:54.400 --> 22:56.860
hurry up and take action about it.

22:58.340 --> 22:59.950
I'm quite satisfied

23:00.040 --> 23:01.600
with Jiang.

23:02.100 --> 23:03.130
He is a good kid,

23:03.750 --> 23:05.150
reliable and dependable.

23:05.710 --> 23:06.570
I approve of him

23:06.630 --> 23:07.510
as my son-in-law.

23:07.530 --> 23:08.170
Okay.

23:08.190 --> 23:09.310
Have you decided what to eat?

23:11.310 --> 23:11.880
Professor Yu,

23:12.750 --> 23:14.330
I think now

23:14.660 --> 23:16.270
that the most important thing is to find

23:16.310 --> 23:17.430
the person who took

23:17.450 --> 23:17.920
Li Ruonan's mother away.

23:21.160 --> 23:23.180
But according to Director Li,

23:23.640 --> 23:24.600
Li Ruonan's mother

23:24.630 --> 23:27.070
was in very poor health at that time.

23:27.990 --> 23:29.040
The fact that someone was able to

23:29.070 --> 23:30.110
take her away in that condition

23:30.710 --> 23:31.640
means that the person

23:31.670 --> 23:32.590
has a very close relationship

23:32.630 --> 23:33.670
with Li Ruonan.

23:35.070 --> 23:36.510
And Li Ruonan also trusts him deeply.

23:37.270 --> 23:38.150
Could it be

23:38.230 --> 23:38.950
one of her relatives?

23:41.280 --> 23:42.500
That's a possibility.

23:44.350 --> 23:45.560
Or perhaps

23:45.830 --> 23:48.270
this person gave Li Ruonan

23:48.670 --> 23:50.430
a very convincing reason,

23:51.470 --> 23:52.240
such as transferring her mother

23:52.270 --> 23:53.550
to a better hospital

23:55.030 --> 23:56.270
for better treatment.

23:56.870 --> 23:58.040
But there are no further

23:58.070 --> 23:59.430
hospital records for her mother.

23:59.790 --> 24:01.150
If Li Ruonan's mother

24:01.230 --> 24:02.500
has already passed away,

24:02.990 --> 24:04.630
and this person has hidden

24:04.650 --> 24:05.370
all the information,

24:06.430 --> 24:07.800
then this person...

24:10.520 --> 24:11.660
Is the person we're looking for?

24:33.430 --> 24:34.120
Professor Yu,

24:34.140 --> 24:35.270
wait for me in the car.

24:36.430 --> 24:37.130
Okay.

24:37.690 --> 24:38.410
Liu Hao.

24:38.880 --> 24:40.090
Make sure to be careful.

24:40.630 --> 24:42.000
If Wang Yifan is really

24:42.070 --> 24:42.950
the one we're looking for,

24:43.420 --> 24:45.210
you mustn't expose yourself.

24:45.460 --> 24:46.530
I'm afraid that he may have

24:46.550 --> 24:48.230
an extreme reaction if he sees you.

24:49.520 --> 24:50.190
Got it.

24:50.230 --> 24:51.030
I'm prepared.

24:52.950 --> 24:53.960
Be very careful!

25:40.110 --> 25:41.110
Today, I'll show you

25:41.110 --> 25:42.270
how to play pool.

25:48.770 --> 25:49.670
Almost, boss.

25:49.790 --> 25:51.120
Almost.

26:32.470 --> 26:33.020
Okay.

26:34.360 --> 26:35.570
You're still the best.

26:38.070 --> 26:38.800
I'm done playing.

26:40.190 --> 26:40.750
You don't want to play anymore?

26:40.780 --> 26:42.030
It's no fun to play with you guys.

26:43.790 --> 26:44.480
Let's go.

27:18.290 --> 27:21.180
[Zai Qing Electronics Co., Ltd.]

27:28.160 --> 27:30.470
[Zai Qing Electronics Co., Ltd.]

27:43.170 --> 27:44.890
[Zai Qing Electronics Co., Ltd.]

28:38.270 --> 28:39.340
Professor Yu.

28:39.990 --> 28:41.500
I'm really sorry.

28:42.230 --> 28:44.200
Someone has paid for your life.

28:45.210 --> 28:46.560
You're so pretty

28:47.460 --> 28:48.700
and have a good figure.

28:49.310 --> 28:50.370
But don't worry.

28:50.430 --> 28:52.000
I'll leave your body in one piece.

31:38.370 --> 31:39.100
Hello?

31:39.470 --> 31:40.840
Run over one of your men.

31:42.560 --> 31:44.760
That celebrity who's often around you.

31:45.400 --> 31:46.150
He came here and appeared

31:46.190 --> 31:47.420
to save that woman.

31:47.790 --> 31:48.740
What should we do?

31:48.910 --> 31:50.450
Then get rid of both of them.

31:51.110 --> 31:52.290
Two people,

31:52.310 --> 31:54.030
the price goes up.

31:55.080 --> 31:55.890
Name your price.

31:59.030 --> 31:59.940
Okay.

32:31.340 --> 32:32.150
What happened?

32:35.150 --> 32:36.340
I'm with the Anshan District Criminal Investigation Unit.

32:38.600 --> 32:39.370
I'll leave it to you.

32:40.630 --> 32:41.160
Don't move.

32:58.560 --> 32:59.410
Let go of me!

33:16.430 --> 33:17.140
Professor Yu?

33:17.360 --> 33:18.060
Professor Yu!

33:23.890 --> 33:25.770
Hello, is this the emergency center?

33:26.310 --> 33:27.790
I'm at 102 Fushou Road.

33:27.810 --> 33:28.910
Someone is injured here.

33:28.830 --> 33:32.180
[Emergency]

33:53.690 --> 33:54.970
Where is Liu Hao?

33:55.100 --> 33:56.500
He's in the car behind.

33:56.880 --> 33:58.160
Did we catch him?

33:59.030 --> 34:00.110
Yes.

34:00.490 --> 34:01.140
Okay.

34:04.870 --> 34:05.910
Are you okay?

34:06.110 --> 34:07.180
Are you hurt?

34:08.760 --> 34:09.659
I'm fine.

34:09.920 --> 34:10.810
It's just a minor injury.

34:13.909 --> 34:15.719
Why did you only show up after following us

34:16.770 --> 34:18.100
for so many days?

34:18.510 --> 34:20.100
You knew I was following you?

34:22.070 --> 34:22.780
Yes.

34:25.060 --> 34:26.250
I also knew

34:27.030 --> 34:28.190
that you were following me,

34:30.000 --> 34:30.989
trying to take revenge,

34:32.219 --> 34:33.000
right?

34:36.440 --> 34:37.900
I did hesitate.

34:39.580 --> 34:40.190
But...

34:40.230 --> 34:41.550
but when I saw that person

34:41.570 --> 34:42.590
trying to kill you,

34:43.690 --> 34:45.190
I didn't think I could just stand by.

34:47.429 --> 34:48.710
I knew it.

34:50.139 --> 34:51.340
I was right about you.

34:53.989 --> 34:55.580
You won't hurt anyone.

34:57.670 --> 34:58.450
Right?

35:10.390 --> 35:11.760
Anyway,

35:13.480 --> 35:15.110
thank you for today.

35:17.330 --> 35:18.720
If it weren't for you,

35:21.150 --> 35:22.780
I might not be alive right now.

35:30.150 --> 35:31.500
D-Do you know...

35:34.020 --> 35:36.760
who sent the person who came to

35:37.990 --> 35:39.210
kill you today?

35:40.100 --> 35:40.850
Who?

35:42.020 --> 35:43.100
It's Wen Peng.

35:45.430 --> 35:46.920
Run over one of your men.

35:47.470 --> 35:49.490
That celebrity who's often around you.

35:49.630 --> 35:51.880
He came and appeared to save that woman.

35:52.020 --> 35:53.120
What should we do?

35:53.240 --> 35:54.670
Then get rid of both of them.

35:57.910 --> 35:59.630
He thought I'd passed out.

36:07.810 --> 36:08.670
He had been lying to me

36:08.670 --> 36:10.070
from the very beginning.

36:11.930 --> 36:13.810
I believed every word he said.

36:18.230 --> 36:19.350
But the words you told me,

36:19.390 --> 36:20.790
I didn't listen to a single one.

36:22.290 --> 36:23.740
That was all because you're a fool.

36:25.400 --> 36:27.240
Wasn't he just taking advantage of

36:27.580 --> 36:28.310
your innocence?

36:34.420 --> 36:35.190
All right.

36:36.810 --> 36:37.910
It's all in the past.

36:41.720 --> 36:42.610
Also,

36:44.330 --> 36:45.950
I owe you an apology...

36:47.890 --> 36:49.290
about your mother.

36:53.420 --> 36:54.570
I'm sorry.

36:56.360 --> 36:57.520
I mean it.

37:00.790 --> 37:02.150
You don't have to apologize to me.

37:08.440 --> 37:09.830
I've come around.

37:12.190 --> 37:13.670
You guys are the police.

37:15.100 --> 37:16.320
From your standpoint,

37:16.350 --> 37:18.030
you did nothing wrong.

37:22.470 --> 37:23.350
It's me who couldn't

37:23.390 --> 37:25.130
get over myself.

37:27.270 --> 37:32.890
[Police]

37:43.180 --> 37:44.340
Yu Bofeng.

37:45.700 --> 37:46.630
I know you won't

37:46.630 --> 37:47.920
contact me again.

37:49.200 --> 37:50.810
I'm afraid that for you,

37:51.640 --> 37:52.880
now,

37:53.730 --> 37:55.610
you don't regard me as your friend anymore.

37:57.980 --> 37:59.970
Even if you hate me

38:00.130 --> 38:01.620
and never want to see me again,

38:01.670 --> 38:03.270
I respect your decision.

38:04.940 --> 38:06.190
But I still want to

38:06.190 --> 38:07.270
explain things to you properly.

38:09.990 --> 38:11.530
As for what happened back then,

38:11.710 --> 38:13.190
you had your standpoint,

38:13.560 --> 38:14.970
and I had mine.

38:16.250 --> 38:17.580
We are not bad people.

38:19.160 --> 38:20.200
We were just

38:20.230 --> 38:21.960
on different sides of things.

38:25.470 --> 38:26.200
It's all in the past now.

38:31.940 --> 38:32.890
Okay.

38:47.990 --> 38:48.510
Captain Jiang.

38:49.170 --> 38:50.350
I caught Wang Yifan.

38:50.880 --> 38:52.390
I'm heading to the Chengzhou Public Security Bureau

38:52.430 --> 38:53.070
to go through the procedure now,

38:53.820 --> 38:55.410
and tomorrow I'll take him back to Ninghai.

38:55.830 --> 38:56.500
Okay.

38:56.640 --> 38:57.370
Good job.

38:57.830 --> 38:58.590
Yu Bofeng said

38:58.670 --> 38:59.480
he heard Wang Yifan

38:59.510 --> 39:00.440
calling Wen Peng.

39:00.630 --> 39:01.920
I checked the number,

39:02.150 --> 39:03.360
and it's not registered under Wen Peng's name.

39:04.630 --> 39:06.590
Wen Peng is very cautious.

39:07.070 --> 39:08.560
He rarely leaves a trail.

39:10.080 --> 39:11.400
How are you

39:11.570 --> 39:12.440
and Professor Yu doing?

39:12.870 --> 39:13.510
I'm fine.

39:14.270 --> 39:15.200
I guess Professor Yu

39:15.230 --> 39:16.330
needs to rest for a few days.

39:16.670 --> 39:17.830
Hao, don't push yourself too hard.

39:17.870 --> 39:18.900
You're still injured.

39:18.920 --> 39:19.510
Don't force yourself.

39:19.660 --> 39:20.350
Don't worry.

39:20.680 --> 39:21.280
I'll be back tomorrow.

39:22.150 --> 39:22.810
